<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 detail-desc\">\n<div class=\"content-fck\">\n<div class=\"content-fck-font-size\">\n<div class=\"box-des-detail this-one\">\n<div class=\"box-des-detail this-one\">\n<p>Sau th\u1eddi gian t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb, \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n Phi Khanh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c cho b\u1ea5m m\u00e1y b\u1ed9 phim &#8220;C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00f3m nh\u1ecf&#8221;, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham gia di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean nh\u00ed H\u1ea1o Khang, Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Vy, c\u00f9ng n\u1eef di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Gia Linh v\u00e0 nam di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Nguy\u1ec5n L\u00e2m. B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh phim quay quanh qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 Khu du l\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam (TP Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang) v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n l\u00e0 Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"detail-content-body\" data-theme=\"0\">\n<p>Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, \u00ca-k\u00edp \u0111o\u00e0n phim \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 v\u00e0 Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho b\u1ed9 phim, nh\u01b0: Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, L\u0103ng Tho\u1ea1i Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea7u, Mi\u1ebfu C\u00f4 N\u0103m, Ch\u00f9a Hang, nh\u00e0 th\u1edd Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt cao 81m, Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc H\u00f2a B\u00ecnh song sinh tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam&#8230;<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_1-1709040795606.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -0\" width=\"1280\" height=\"891\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_1-1709040795606.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>\u00ca-k\u00edp b\u1ed9 phim &#8220;C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n x\u00f3m nh\u1ecf&#8221; t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<p>Kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n t\u1eeb TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c l\u00e2n c\u1eadn sau khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 hay th\u00f4ng tin \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 gh\u00e9 tham quan v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean trong \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim. Sau \u0111\u00f3, du kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc, xin l\u1ed9c v\u00e0 check-in nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n Phi Khanh cho bi\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim s\u1ebd ghi l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh ho\u00e0ng h\u00f4n, tr\u0103ng s\u00e1ng, c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111o\u00e0n s\u1ebd ghi nh\u1eadn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 khuya \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00eam t\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0: Nh\u1ea1c n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed \u1edf mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y, ca c\u1ed5 giao duy\u00ean h\u00e1t v\u1edbi nhau, c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2n gian, do \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00f4 t\u00f4 C\u00f4 3 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, nh\u1eb1m mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f3n \u0103n tinh th\u1ea7n, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u0103n h\u00f3a trong m\u00f9a l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i V\u00eda B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u0103m nay.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_2-1709040809701.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -0\" width=\"1042\" height=\"701\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_2-1709040809701.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>C\u00e1c di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean check-in d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<p>Theo Ban Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, hi\u1ec7n n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh cho c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt. Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam r\u1ea5t hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim, nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch qu\u1ea3ng b\u00e1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, con ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam v\u00e0 TP Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, An Giang.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_3-1709040829250.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -0\" width=\"853\" height=\"580\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_3-1709040829250.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam v\u00e0 qu\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 Khu du l\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00ca-k\u00edp ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh cho b\u1ed9 phim.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_4-1709040830546.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -1\" width=\"813\" height=\"536\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_4-1709040830546.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_5-1709040829515.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -2\" width=\"912\" height=\"601\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_5-1709040829515.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_6-1709040829593.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111o\u00e0n l\u00e0m phim ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh -3\" width=\"656\" height=\"440\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_6-1709040829593.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/27\/Hinh_8-1709040829843.jpg\" alt=\"Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N